title: Plackers Twin-Line Dental Flossers, Cool Mint Flavor, Dual Action Flossing System, Easy Storage, Super Tuffloss, 2X The Clean, 75 Count
description: Floss like a boss! Clean twice as nice with Plackers Twin-Line Dental Flossers. Get 2X the clean with dual strands of Super Tuffloss. Our patented twin-line dual action flossing system allows you to use two lines of floss to help dislodge trapped food and debris between your teeth. The easy grip handle provides more control and comfort while cleaning between your teeth and gums. Rely on Plackers to Get the Gunk Out. Enjoy fresh breath with cool mint flavor. Perfect for on-the-go or at-home dental care with easy storage and consumer preferred zipper close. Includes 75 dental flossers. Smile Like Everyone's Watching.
